w."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The theme provides all tokens which defines in the end the rendering of everything."}],"url":"\/tutorials\/oudsthemescontract\/tutorial-2-instanciate-theme"},"doc://OUDSThemesContract/tutorials/OUDSThemesContract/tutorial-6-going-further":{"title":"Going further with more resources","kind":"project","type":"topic","estimatedTime":"10min","role":"project","url":"\/tutorials\/oudsthemescontract\/tutorial-6-going-further","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorials\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorial-6-going-further","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Since you have learnt how OUDS works with theme, themeable view, components, tuning and vieww modifiers, it is time now to discover some online resources."}]},"doc://OUDSThemesContract/tutorials/OUDSThemesContract/tutorial-5-styling-things":{"role":"project","title":"Styling things","type":"topic","kind":"project","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorials\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorial-5-styling-things","estimatedTime":"30min","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Even if components increase the identity of your apps, it is not enough. Typography, fonts and tokens are here to improve that."}],"url":"\/tutorials\/oudsthemescontract\/tutorial-5-styling-things"},"doc://OUDSThemesContract/tutorials/OUDSThemesContract/tutorial-3-use-first-components":{"title":"Use your first OUDS components","type":"topic","kind":"project","estimatedTime":"30min","role":"project","url":"\/tutorials\/oudsthemescontract\/tutorial-3-use-first-components","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorials\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorial-3-use-first-components","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"OUDS provides components ready to be used, specified in Figma assets and preventing users to handle tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"They are rendered thanks to the theme in use."}]},"ic_component_intro.png":{"type":"image","alt":"Logo of OUDS","variants":[{"url":"\/images\/OUDSThemesContract\/ic_component_intro.png","traits":["1x","light"]}],"identifier":"ic_component_intro.png"},"doc://OUDSThemesContract/tutorials/OUDSThemesContract/tutorial-1-package-and-librairies":{"role":"project","title":"Swift Package integration","type":"topic","kind":"project","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorials\/OUDSThemesContract\/tutorial-1-package-and-librairies","estimatedTime":"10min","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"OUDS iOS is exposed through an open source Swift Package hosted on GitHub, and provides several librairies for your needs."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"These librairies help to split products and make users able to select only what they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"SwiftUI is the only official supported framework."}],"url":"\/tutorials\/oudsthemescontract\/tutorial-1-package-and-librairies"}}}